sentences: Carlie Hanson (born May 18, 2000) is an American singer-songwriter.
In 2018, she released the song "Only One", which garnered attention after being featured on a playlist curated by Taylor Swift.
She released her debut extended play, Junk, in June 2019.
This was followed by her 2020 extended play, DestroyDestroyDestroyDestroy.
